title: Tatta, Tank
text:
Tatta is an administrative unit, known as <a href="Union%20councils%20of%20Pakistan">Union council</a>, of <a href="Tank%20District">Tank District</a> in the <a href="Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa">Khyber Pakhtunkhwa</a> province of <a href="Pakistan">Pakistan</a>.
District Tank has 1 <a href="Tehsils">Tehsils</a> i.e. Tank. Each tehsil comprises certain numbers of union councils. There are 16 union councils in district Tank.
